snippet.textDisplay:
Hey Alex, I love your videos and thank you for putting so much effort into them for our entertainment.

I wanted to ask you, if you would ever do an animated video of your Japan story? From 18 to where you are now?

I appreciate its a years long story 😂 but I loved your older videos and the ones about your story honestly I found really inspiring.

Currently trying to rebuild my life at 27, I’ve made some poor decisions but had some incredible experiences. At the moment your two videos that you made about how you turned your life around keep giving me inspiration and make me grounded.

You have inspired me to teach myself some new skills. I recently started teaching myself some IT certifications as I have lots of free time in between applying for jobs at my folks place.

Either way thank you for your videos it would mean the world to me if you reply to my comment. But I totally understand if you are too busy to respond.

Stay awesome Alex.
